人路，d人隨時用英文答你添呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"10678f79e9f21243d5ac391f9ed3c172d12199c0","tid":296363,"uid":80267,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-24T15:03:15.000Z","msg":"都痴撚線 成街啲幼稚園小學生甚至初中雞都用蝗語溝通 梗係唔洗自己去學啦 根本平時日常生活都講 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 第時新一代應該冇人識廣東話<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"48f7370dc75e454cfc6641cbb8a7426922e15594","tid":296363,"uid":36178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-24T15:03:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>幅圖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n小姐 睡覺一晚多少錢 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n廣東話粗口<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"39507fef130679eb9dceea6896c1537afa481702","tid":296363,"uid":124899,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-24T15:04:37.000Z","msg":"上面果句實用好多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cd937e2fa99250e4fb4c7f881e6594b981488641","tid":296363,"uid":68728,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-24T15:05:34.000Z","msg":"而家新一代啲母語係普通話啦 洗撚搵你學咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"14fc65c2f2b078d14e123a72aa40bfb07d2d4d32","tid":296363,"uid":36178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-24T15:06:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>普通話使鬼學咩？就算學都學台灣國語啦</blockquote><br />\n國語研習社改名做普通話研習社<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7953ebe90760bec4c61bca5d35d1f57a535735a3","tid":296363,"uid":8858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-24T15:26:50.000Z","msg":"香港係講粵語同英文<br />\n本地人用支那話,我屌你老母呀"},{"pid":"993fd94afc55c5bb5dc44af35fa93d86ec1b8f13","tid":296363,"uid":6799,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-24T15:39:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>香港係講粵語同英文<br />\n本地人用支那話,我屌你老母呀</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"18c6683fce7e4f4a10d6d9032666a81b114cddc8","tid":296363,"uid":57170,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-24T15:47:23.000Z","msg":"老老豆豆 <br />\n<br />\n英文差書你都冇得讀<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/36.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n出黎做野 普通話差最多聽果個辛苦  (唔係做SALESMAN既話)<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n最理想 英文學到劉家傑     普通話講到曹仁超咁樣"},{"pid":"5c17726848b1117a45631e8b8996c0fdeb565465","tid":296363,"uid":37413,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-24T15:49:09.000Z","msg":"弱撚智， 你有大量人力物力資源， 又官方又強制， 本土派有得比？ 如果啲人咁都唔學就係你哋問題啦， 返去檢討吓， 乜都瀨"},{"pid":"d78f556abe473ecbbcc1274871e01047cc650851","tid":296363,"uid":53026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-24T15:50:36.000Z","msg":"認真，香港政府有無正式提供廣東話教育？否則新來港人士大條道理唔學本地話。"},{"pid":"c9e8ad3dd94c4c81a49dda433b6dde1816811565","tid":296363,"uid":53223,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-24T15:56:04.000Z","msg":"有錢有時間學多幾個英文好過啦，就連政府自己話就話鼓勵普通話，實情水9你班傻仔。<br />\n<br />\n內部咪一樣英文為準，英文第一。個個老細出email都係寫英文，高層會議都係講英文。<br />\n<br />\n以前就話自由行嚟消費咩咩咩，都有少少動力去學幾句賺錢，而家根本唔需要。<br />\n<br />\n香港人最現實嫁啦，冇用就冇需要學，好正常，而家普通話水平低對經濟生活完全冇影響。"},{"pid":"140c27ce6b282ebcac7b036055235509285b73b5","tid":296363,"uid":51183,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-24T16:09:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>好多香港人普通話真係唔得，國內同胞問路都唔識答，好可悲</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n識都唔答，吹呀??<br />\n我成日響街被強國人問路<br />\n用普通話問照答廣東話<br />\n聽得明就明<br />\n唔明就關我鳩事<br />\n<br />\n利申:台灣朋友完全聽得明我既國語"},{"pid":"3db9c1092c982f16bc8bc3ecbcd76db6553bd72e","tid":296363,"uid":79442,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-24T16:13:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>好多香港人普通話真係唔得，國內同胞問路都唔識答，好可悲</blockquote><br />\n台灣人帶佢去都得，大陸人就一定扮唔識"},{"pid":"20b9f939cb06137b8bff8fe27edf8ba8f1c0f5df","tid":296363,"uid":111425,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-24T16:14:15.000Z","msg":"有柒用咩<br />\n依d班細路同緊蝗語傾計嫁啦<br />\n我覺得下兩代就唔識廣東話"},{"pid":"8056d4e1f470687c236b6e9c9719e01cf15ba1a4","tid":296363,"uid":71008,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-24T16:16:04.000Z","msg":"做文明人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2f57657a68561fa40ac1e08adaa0aeae8b72a3b3","tid":296363,"uid":53705,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-24T16:26:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>認真，香港政府有無正式提供廣東話教育？否則新來港人士大條道理唔學本地話。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n就算有得學, 佢地都大條道理唔學<br />\n<br />\n例如<br />\n新移民: 「香港是中國一部份, 用普通話很正常, 為什麼要學廣東話??」"},{"pid":"663804a161dc6fa9284805ff3cf4a28db9bd9952","tid":296363,"uid":20856,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-24T16:32:12.000Z","msg":"冇必要就支那人，唔止問路，就算工作場合，我照講廣東話，佢地根本聽得明，極其量會請我講慢啲，但其實完全唔使講匪語。<br />\n<br />\n真係唔撚明香港人奴到點樣嘅地步，你去日本都唔會要人地講廣東話啦，自己反而樣樣嘢就哂人，周圍啲廣播一定係要加埋匪語，根本粵英雙語就夠。<br />\n<br />\n英語係國際語言，匪語唔係，廣播有英語好正常，唔該五毛收檔。"},{"pid":"093e77962209094f6457322ac22e149a3fc20b86","tid":296363,"uid":52605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-24T16:36:24.000Z","msg":"其實學普通話人數跌係因為單雙非果堆人大量上升<br />\n呢堆人唔會去學普通話啩"},{"pid":"686c195bec512e1220983ef001aec2f2bd5440e7","tid":296363,"uid":23180,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-24T17:17:34.000Z","msg":"比支那人搶完飯碗教蝗話仲要屈番落香港人政治度<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n支那人個格就係咁衰"},{"pid":"6a180b0c85b69ff17c0834a241f60112ec447742","tid":296363,"uid":41245,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-24T17:21:56.000Z","msg":"政府幾時保障返依啲人嘅利益減炒返學校學普通話？<br />\n的士佬有要保障，噉佢地呢？"},{"pid":"4341f559ce800157f78efc2cfed9b162d67f8ad4","tid":296363,"uid":11753,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"c